    "body" : "<p>If you are using <em>drawableStart</em>, <em>drawableEnd</em>, <em>drawableTop</em> or <em>drawableBottom</em>; you must use \"<strong>setCompoundDrawablesRelativeWithIntrinsicBounds</strong>\"</p>\n\n<pre><code>edittext.setCompoundDrawablesRelativeWithIntrinsicBounds(0, 0, R.drawable.anim_search_to_close, 0)\n</code></pre>\n"
